title: Add a deposit fee to all gardens except PLANT
body:
We are proposing to add a deposit fee to all gardens except PLANT garden.

To be more clear, this will be for BUSD, USDC and CAKE gardens.

We are suggesting a deposit fee of 1%

The deposit fee will be use to buy back PLANT at market price and burn them, as well as fund the PlantSwap Development Fund.
choices: Yes add a deposit fee of 1%
